The SyntaxDiagramMojo can be configured like this:

<plugins>
  <plugin>
    <groupId>de.banapple.maven</groupId>
    <artifactId>railroaddiagram-maven-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
    <configuration>
      <grammarFile>src/main/antlr/mygrammar.g</grammarFile>
    </configuration>
  </plugin>
</plugins>

Usage:
# mvn railroaddiagram:generate

This will create an index.html and image files in the folder
target/antlrdiagrams 
by default.
